body_html:
The null asset error indicates that the model is not being found in the assets/ dir.

This is currently missing from the directions (needs to be added), but if you're not building with Bazel you'll need to download and extract the contents of https://storage.googleapis.com/download.tensorflow.org/models/stylize_v1.zip into the assets/ dir.
